---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — Ohad Israeli">
  <section class="intro">
    <p class="signature">$ cat about.md</p>
    <h1>About</h1>
  </section>

  <div class="prose">
    <p>
      Hi, I'm Ohad. I work on data streaming and distributed systems. This site is
      a running log of the things I build — some are quick experiments, others have
      a full repository of code and docs behind them.
    </p>

    <h2>How this site is organized</h2>
    <p>
      Each project gets its own article under <a href="/projects">/projects</a>.
      When a project has substantial code, it lives in its own GitHub repository and
      the article links straight to it. Smaller experiments live entirely in the
      write-up.
    </p>

    <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>GitHub — <a href="https://github.com/ohad-israeli" target="_blank" rel="me noopener">github.com/ohad-israeli</a></li>
      <li>RSS — <a href="/rss.xml">subscribe to new projects</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
